Interface TypedBufferedMutator<T>

    public interface TypedBufferedMutator<T>
extends org.apache.hadoop.hbase.client.BufferedMutator
    Just a typed wrapper around BufferedMutator used to ensure that columns can write only to the table mutator for the right table.
